text: Apni dosti kaafi late hui bhai par achha hai hui. Thanks for all the respect bhai, uss din mazaa hi laa diya tune, Mishra ki kya maari hai. Ab to kaha hum yaad rhenge USA jo jaana hai waha bhi aadhi bottle pee pee ke logo ki maarte rehna. Ye sirf tujhse bol rha hu ki do not stay humble, do not underestimate yourself, kismat tere saath hai. Aur maths to favorite subject hai hi tera, padhte rehna class chhod ke nikal mat jaana.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: ‚ÄúAaj to kahi chal le yaar‚Äù. Tujhe shanti hi nhi rehti thi bhai kabhi, roz kahi chalo. Par agar ye attitude na hota to itna ghum hi nhi paate. Koi trip tere bina imagine hi nhi kar sakta main bhai. Delhi ho ya Goa ya Rishikesh ya Shimla, par ye to bas shuruat hai aane waale time ki jab trip pe trip padhti raha karegi. Orchha hi reh gaya yaar end tak, par waha to solo trip hi maar le. You are the nicest person I met in the campus, aur arrangement me expert. Music ka arrangement, light ka arrangement, kuch bhi party-related bolo to ho jaaye. CCD se kab Anaicha‚Äôs hua aur kab Goa pata hi nhi chala. Wo accident yaad hai na jab Abhishek hospital gaye the. Aur wo maal ke baad thand lagna, jisne poori raat kharaab kar di thi. Topa chori ho gaya tha bhai par aisi 100 raatein kurbaan hai. Wo din bhi acche se yaad hai jab jab roye hai kisi baat ko lekar, especially college khatam hone ke. But these things aside, mujhe life me kabhi bhi kuch kaam padhega to sabse pehla phone tujhe hi jayega bhai. First year Antaragni ke condoms se leke wo bahut dur ke open mic se leke final year ki aakhri party tak sab kuch saath kiya hai bhai. Itne saare nightouts maare hai, RM tak ko nhi chhoda bhai. Itni bets lagayi hai, vaccine waali to bachi hai abhi aur books waali bhul mat jaana ‚Äúhehe‚Äù. Wo video to safe rhega mere pass most probably. I could say anything I want to you. Meethi si wo gaali teri sunne ko tayyar hu main. Honestly speaking, I will wish for a friend like you wherever I go, aur kya hi bolu bhai.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Zyada to ghume nhi campus me par jab bhi mile hai kaafi warmth feel hui. Ek alag hi apna pan sa lagta hai bhai. Bahut badhiya aadmi ho tum. Saath me Indore bhi bahut kam aaye apan par jo ek time aaye the usme hi main ye baat samajh gaya tha. Cravings ki to kya hi baat karu bhai main, badhte badhte bahut badh gayi hai. Jald hi milte hai ghar se nikalke.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: kya hai lodu
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Khushkismati hai ye meri ki tere jaisa panauti aadmi meri life me aaya. First year se kaafi hangout karta tha tu ground floor pe and that was the best thing that could have happened. Bol bol ke thak gaya tha Bechara ki coding karne chalo koi saath me, akela karke aa jaata tha dhokebaaz. Bahut annoying aur irritating aadmi hai yaar tu par kabhi mat bhulna ‚ÄúSonu, tune humre pe bharosa kahe nai ke.‚Äù Itna sehen karne ke saath saath kitne to assignment kiye hai yaar. Aur har course ke saath kuch na kuch incident hai, jaise ‚Äúye O hai ya 0‚Äù. CS220 to tu mere bina nikal hi nhi pata, power cable to maine hi connect ki thi humesha :sunglasses:. Galaxy waala poora sem to tere upar hi chhod diya tha. Tu agar na hota to aaj kasam se degree nhi nikalti. Cannot imagine college without you. Aise helpful log bahut kam hote hai duniya main par apne baare me thoda to sab hi sochte hai. Itna entertain kiya hai first year se apni marwake, I am astonished. Chaar log khade ho aur saath me tu ho to aur kisi ki maarte hi nhi hai log, kuch special effect hai ye tera. But that is because people love you, cutest Y17 male hai bhai tu wo bhi aisi shakal ke saath, hidden compliment hai ye. Altu faltu ki cheezein bhi bahut mangwayi hai tune, kabhi dab karta hua penguin to kabhi use and throw stuff. Ek baat ka dukh hai par first time mere saamne nhi gaali baki tune lodu. Zindagi me kabhi bhi code nhi likhayega to tere pass hi aaunga, bada aadmi banke bhul mat jaana Noogler. Bahut Maria milti rhe tujhe aur gaanja bhi milta rhe, yehi duaa karunga.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: I remember the orientation time, tab apni zyada baat nhi hoti thi, bas adjacent seats thi. But uske baad apni kaafi achhi friendship ho gayi. I also remember the walk we had after CCD one day when you were a bit stressed, we also came close like our names and our birthdays. We should meet soon again in the walk of life.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: You are quite friendly, and you sing very well. We were not that close, but I was happy to help you whenever I got that chance. I still remember the walk we had from OAT that day. Remain pure as you are, maybe we get to go on a trip together again.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: You are a pleasant person. I remember you used to sit in the front and attend every lecture, at least all those I had been to. We will definitely do big things in life starting from, six-pack abs for both of us. When we meet in the walk of life, teach me basketball.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Kuch baatein hai sir jo yaha likhi nhi jaa sakti bas samjhi jaa sakti hai, samajh rhe ho na üòä. Kaafi enjoy kari hai mehfilein aapke saath. Kuch logo se vibe match ho jaati hai ekdum se, wohi baat hai. Bas ye bata do ki Jessica koun hai, curiousity khatam hi nhi ki aapne. IIM me 2 states bana dena sir.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Jab mai first time tujhse mila tha to mujhe dekhke laga tha ki kaafi attitude hoga tujhme, but then you moved to our wing and you were friendly and warm. Snow world waala din yaad hai, jab bean bag me se surprise nikla tha. Keep posing for photos like you do.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: When we met in the first year, I started liking you instantly. I still remember when we went to the hospital for your leg and the conversation, we had that time. I hope it heals soon so we can do more things together instead of just a Rangoli making session which I failed to be a part of. Stay connected and we meet soon, iss baar achhe se üòä.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: You are the sweetest person I got to know on campus. You care a lot for others‚Äô feelings and that is a thing which is growing very rare these days. Remain as pleasant as you are, aur ek photoshoot drone se mera bhi karwa do kabhi.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Bhai memes banane ke expert to ho hi tum. Kitna randi rona kiya hai bhai courses ko leke 4 saal ye apne ko pata hi hai. Especially CS252 waali raat jab sab log baithke apne apne app bana rhe the. Milte hai bhai phirse, drunk Gosai ko dekhne ka mann hai dobara.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Waise to we are from the same city, but we came here as acquaintances. We got into a petty fight and then one walk changed everything. I have got many defining moments from being with you and learnt a lot about life. You broaden my perspective. I have had 21 birthdays till now, but no one did anything special compared to what you did, you made me feel special that day with your excellent craft skills. Delhi ki wo trip humesha yaad rhegi, but the best time would undoubtedly be the time we spent in Mumbai. I hope you remember the horse ride. But above the big things in life, I value the small things we had, especially the painting of minions which I had to complete as you were not that good a painter. And also, the little notes you used to leave for me at unexpected places. It was a new experience for me to be in a relationship and I realised that it was the thing that was missing because I got you, you completed my life in the campus. Fire department ke saath waala incidence to main kabhi nhi bhulunga, aur na hi marine drive pe wo baithna, jaha aisa laga ki waqt ruk hi jaata to achha hota. Kaafi competitive spirit hai tujhme jo lifelong maintain rakhna hai (in a healthy way *wink*). We spent a lot of time in many different places. Kabhi RM, kabhi library, kabhi GH, but the best was the skywalk, and a close second is the Earth Science building. Wo road bhi achhi hai jo library se RM tak jaati hai. I respect you for the progress you have made since the first year. Poori journey kaafi achhi rahi but I still wish we had met earlier and got more time in the campus. Call me when you want, call me when you need. Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom.
author: Anany  Sharma

author: Anany  Sharma

text: Badhiya aadmi ho yaar Pandey tum. Achha hua SPO me chale gaye to itni help ho gayi, warna cheezein hi samajh nhi aati bahut time tak. Bahut shareef lage the jab first time mile the par ab pata hai bade haraami ho beta. Mishra ki maarte raho to sukhi rhoge.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Bhai Galaxy ki practice me bahut mazaa aata tha. Samveg the to ho bhi gaya, apan dono to shaayad nhi kar paate XD. Kaafi multi-talented ho bhai, baaki cheezein chhod mat dena aur dosto ko bataya karo koi ladki ka chakkar ho to. Kaliyon ka Chaman reh gaya yaar perform karna aur saath hi reh gaya Aari Aari.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Sabse rational aur practical insaan hai tu but with that, tu bahut saare groups me gel bhi kar leta hai. Genuine respect hai bhai tere liye. You also know that line between fun and work perfectly, ye bahut rare hai apne college me. You can also stand up to anyone and fight for the right cause. First year ki endless debates se leke third year ke political dilemma tak kaafi discussions hue and sab me bahut mazaa aaya. Mujhe to wo disturbing night yaad hai jab Abhishek apne ko thand lag gayi thi aur apan dono ko waha sofe pe sona padha tha. Dono trips pe bahut mazaa aaya bhai, aur maarte rhenge trips. The best thing about you is that you are always up for adventure especially jab Abhishek aur Swapnil bhi kat gaye the (remember the reference). USA jaake hum logo ko bhul mat jaana bhai tujhe hi bulana hai waha ghumane ke liye.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: When we first met, you had those teacher vibes. Jaise kuch galat(inappropriate) kar denge to scolding ho jaayegi CCD ki main table pe. Par when I got to know you, you were nothing like that but just a nice person who I could connect with. I wish hum kisi ke through nhi mile hote though, aur apna dance to reh hi gaya.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Reels sirf shoot ki tune, ek me aa bhi jaata. Tere karan enjoyable ho gaya reels shoot karna. Galaxy bhi kar leta saath me, par in the hindsight achha hi hai nhi kiya *wink*. Politics karwate raho logo ko, kaafi achha aur clean word hai. Apna naam sahi jagah use karo, kaafi tarakki milegi.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: You are the nicest person who knows everything about the campus. Logo ki gossip chahiye ho ya pata karna ho senate me kya chal rha hai, tujhe sab pata rehta hai. Batate rehna bas aise hi khabrein. Aur bhand aaram se hua kar, uss din Antaragni me kaisi haalat ho gayi thi tera, but everything happens for a reason üòä.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: I remember how we first met through Kushagra and later we went out together for work I had. I would always remember the small trip we had out of campus then. We had a lot of fun on campus and it was always fun hanging out with you. Let's meet soon.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Bhai Rishikesh aur Goa dono trips pe bahut mazaa aaya tere saath. Are Delhi to main bhul hi gaya tha. I still remember ki tune KTM chalwayi thi Goa me, mazaa aa gaya tha uss din. Stay smart as always, mehengi daaru peete rahenge saath me.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: You are one of the most pleasant people I have met in our branch with a bright future ahead. Also, you have that smart and sassy software engineer look, like you could hack NASA while drinking a beer. Dance karte hai plan kabhi, saath me karenge, milte hai kabhi in the walk of life.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Baal bahut achhe color karwaye par tiktok star banne ki koshish nhi ki yaar tune. Drawing itni badhiya banayi thi ladki ki apne room me ki famous ho gayi wo drawing. Jitney logo ko main jaanta hu unme best hai tu drawing aur designing me. Still, the best thing about you is ki tune mana nhi kiya kabhi kahi jaane me, koi bhi trip ho ya kahi bhi jaa rhe ho. This speaks in terms of solidarity, tab bhi jab Abhishek aur Swapnil kat gaye the(reference). First year ki antaragni ka wo fuck up bhi humesha yaad rhega, condoms laana kaam nhi aaya uss din. ‚ÄúHume gussa aa gaya tha‚Äù to main kabhi nhi bhulunga. Alag alag colour karwate raho baalo ko, kabhi saath me karwayenge kuch green ya neon ka shade aur wo first year waali video delete kardo ab.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: First year me chaadar ke neeche rone ke baad se bahut progress ki hai tune uss aspect of life me. Mujhe yaad hai gym jaane ke baad kya hua that teri kamar ke saath aur phir nurse ko dekh ke kaise sab theek ho gaya tha. Phir se try karna kabhi gym jaane ki. Yaad hai uss din ML waale assignment me rolls lene 5 log gaye the gate pe. Anyways, tu agar videos shoot nhi karta to aaj peeche dekhne ko hi kuch nhi hota. Aur apna room bhi itna saaf rakhta tu, kaise kar lete ho yaar safai. Yaad hai na Antaragni me kaisi haalat hui thi daaru peeke, aur uske baad Goa me. Bahut mazaa aaya tha yaar Goa me, aur trips maarte rhenge. Jab humare saath Goa gaya tha to beach pe akela hi so gaya tha, jab humare bina gaya to kisi aur ke saath, par beach pe sota zaroor hai tu. Ek trip aur banani padhegi bhai, ghar pe raha nhi jaa rha.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Aur Ratnesh Bhai, kaafi achha laga tha tumse milkar jab hum log drams me involved rehte the fresher's ke time pe. Bahut achhe insaan ho tum, stay as pleasant as you are. Aur thanks for helping me in the elections. College me to zyada mile nhi paaye ab banate hai program.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Bhai dono trips pe bahut mazaa aaya tere saath, Goa bhi aur Rishikesh bhi. Especially mujhe wo incident bahut ache se yaad hai jab tu aur Pritu airport chale gaye the casino se and it was an 80km drive that too drunk. Kismat se wapas pahuch gaye tum log.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Kya hi bolu bhai main, 4 me se 3 saal sab kuch saath me hi karte rhe kyunki first year tak apni dosti nhi hui thi warna wo bhi poora saath hi guzarta. Mujhe bahi tak yaad hai CS202 ke assignment me semantic tableaux banana tha aur prayas ke bachho ki dance performance thi, tab main tere pass laptop chhod ke gaya tha aur tune debug kar diya tha ek submittable level tak. Wo to bas shuruat thi pata nhi kitne assignments ki, kaafi help hui yaar. Mujhe to wo bhi yaad hai jab apan teeno ne flexi me aag laga di thi, kya phati thi bhai tab. Tu ekdum dependable aur responsible aadmi hai, jab bhi life me kuch dilemma aaegi to I will definitely consult you. Genuinely shareef aur helpful insaan hai bhai tu, I think sab ki help karne ki koshish karta hai tu. Ummeed hai sab planning jaisa hi ho Hyderabad me. Chess khelte rhenge yaar online, mental health ke hisaab se. Ek trip banti hai yaar saath me, wohi reh gaya hai ab bas.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Sir, jo content apne diya hai na nasho ke baad, uss level ki cheez to kisi stand-up me bhi nhi mili. Exact lines likhne ki soch rha tha par phir laga ho sakta hai kids bhi dekhe aapke future me, isliye avoid kiya. Aapki soch hi alag hai aur ek innate leadership quality hai saari bakchodiyon ke saath. Politics me ghusne ka try karo humse bhi kuch karwa dena, karyakarta ban jayenge.
author: Anany  Sharma

text:
Hey SidJay,

It has been a pleasure getting to know you. You are the most hard-working and industrious person I met in the campus. I have not seen a more academically organized person than you.
We could not do more assignments together because you left Hall 2 to be a part of the KD gang, yet you felt like someone who could be asked for help. Sorry for disturbing you many nights which I know we definitely did unknowingly. 
Thanks for believing that I could go on the silver screen, but do you really think CS stuff is boring? Anyways I have left it to you now.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Bhai apne andar ka keeda marne mat dena. Nayi cheezein try karte rho aur swag maintain rakho. Waise bhi 2 minute ki besharmi hai, yaadein to humesha ki rehti hai. Bahut badhiya aadmi ho be tum. Prank call yaad rakhna bhai humesha, Abdul Gafur ka phone Singapore se bhi aa sakta hai.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Bhai, tumhari zulfein hi aisi hai, tumke hi sabse pehle bulaya jayega opportunity aate hi.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Almost everyone came with friends from their coaching classes but some of the friendships fizzled. I am glad, apna case aisa nhi tha. Bahut dependable aadmi hai tu, abhi to campus aaya nhi par L20 ki chat waala photoshoot yaad hai ki nhi? Jaldi territory mark karo aur mujhe bhi bula liya karo ghumne kabhi. Ek portfolio shoot banta hai kabhi, baad me jab hum milenge aur zaroor milenge, memory slot bana le tu abhi se. Tera nickname yaha reveal kardu kya? Chhodte hai abhi usko, ek trip banate hai fatafat wildlife photography karke aayenge thodi.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: First year me roommate bana tha tu mera aur tujhse baat karke mujhe laga ki ye aaya kaise IIT me itni slow RAM ke saath but you turned out to be a wonderful and entertaining person. Gaand hi phat gayi jab maalum pada ki research paper nikal rha hai par you can do anything you put your mind to. First week me hi apna signature step karke tune apna nickname Hall-2 ke itihas me sunehre aksharo se likh diya, main usko avoid kar rha hu kyunki shaayad kids padhe ye baad me. Blue world ki trip ka somersault humesha yaad rhega bhai mujhe, aur wo surprise bhi jo tune Abhishek ki party pe diya tha. Sutte marwa lo bhai kitni bhi maar loge tum, par asli herogiri phoophoo karne me nhi. Hasa hasa ke pet dukhaya hai tumne bahut baar. Aise hi hasaate rehna Battery Bhai, apni KTM pe baithke. And rule no.1 we do not talk about Fight Club. Poori college life different hoti agar tu na hota. Kal hi wo video dekha jisme tujhe aur Mishra ko bhidaya tha, bahut mazaa aata tha bhai. Ab college life khatam ho gayi hai wo App uninstall kar do ab. Ummeed hai jaldi hi Gym ka asar dikhega, tumpe bhi aur humpe bhi.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Bhai bahut interesting intern thi NYO jo tumhare bina nhi ho paati. Kaise kar lete ho itna WebD. You are one of the most genuine people in our branch. Touch me rehna, ek website humare liye bhi bana dena kabhi.
author: Anany  Sharma
